"-1\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">[Full Text]</font></a> <font size=\"-2\" face=\"arial,helvetica\"></font>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <a href=\"/vir/content/89/1/1\"><font size=\"-1\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">[PDF]</font></a> <font size=\"-2\" face=\"arial,helvetica\"></font></nobr></font></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td nowrap=\"\"></td>\n      <td nowrap=\"\"></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>&nbsp;</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\"><font size=\"-1\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">2.</font>&nbsp;</td>\n      <td colspan=\"2\"><font size=\"-1\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">Sonia Van Dooren, Vedapuri Shanmugam, Vinod Bhullar, Bharat Parekh, Anne-Mieke Vandamme, Walid Heneine, William M. Switzer</font></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td nowrap=\"\"></td>\n      <td nowrap=\"\"></td>\n      <th align=\"left\"><font size=\"-1\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">Identification in gelada baboons (<i>Theropithecus gelada</i>) of a distinct simian T-cell lymphotropic virus type 3 with a broad range of Western blot reactivity</font></th>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td nowrap=\"\"></td>\n      <td nowrap=\"\"></td>\n      <td><font size=\"-1\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">J. Gen. Virol. Feb 01, 2004; 85: 507-519.<br>\n      (In \"ANIMAL: RNA VIRUSES\")&nbsp;&nbsp; <nobr><font size=\"-1\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">[Abstract]</font> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <font size=\"-1\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">[Full Text]</font> <font size=\"-2\" face=\"arial,helvetica\"></font>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <font size=\"-1\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">[PDF]</font> <font size=\"-2\" face=\"arial,helvetica\"></font></nobr></font></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td nowrap=\"\"></td>\n      <td nowrap=\"\"></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>&nbsp;</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\"><font size=\"-1\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">3.</font>&nbsp;</td>\n      <td colspan=\"2\"><font size=\"-1\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">Priti Kumar, Venkatramana D. Krishna, Paramadevanapalli Sulochana, Gejjehalli Nirmala, Maganti Haridattatreya, Vijaya Satchidanandam</font></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td nowrap=\"\"></td>\n      <td nowrap=\"\"></td>\n      <th align=\"left\"><font size=\"-1\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">Cell-mediated immune responses in healthy children with a history of subclinical infection with <i>Japanese encephalitis virus</i>: analysis of CD4<sup>+</sup> and CD8<sup>+</sup> T cell target specificities by intracellular delivery of viral proteins using the human immunodeficiency virus Tat protein transduction domain</font></th>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td nowrap=\"\"></td>\n      <td nowrap=\"\"></td>\n      <td><font size=\"-1\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">J. Gen. Virol. Feb 01, 2004; 85: 471-482.<br>\n      (In \"ANIMAL: RNA VIRUSES\")&nbsp;&nbsp; <nobr><font size=\"-1\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">[Abstract]</font> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <font size=\"-1\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">[Full Text]</font> <font size=\"-2\" face=\"arial,helvetica\"></font>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <font size=\"-1\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">[PDF]</font> <font size=\"-2\" face=\"arial,helvetica\"></font></nobr></font></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td nowrap=\"\"></td>\n      <td nowrap=\"\"></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>&nbsp;</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\"><font size=\"-1\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">4.</font>&nbsp;</td>\n      <td colspan=\"2\"><font size=\"-1\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">Juan Carlos Espinosa, Mónica Morales, Joaquín Castilla, Mark Rogers, Juan María Torres</font></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td nowrap=\"\"></td>\n      <td nowrap=\"\"></td>\n      <th align=\"left\"><font size=\"-1\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">Progression of prion infectivity in asymptomatic cattle after oral bovine spongiform encephalopathy challenge</font></th>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td nowrap=\"\"></td>\n      <td nowrap=\"\"></td>\n      <td><font size=\"-1\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">J. Gen. Virol. Apr 01, 2007; 88: 1379-1383.<br>\n      (In \"OTHER AGENTS\")&nbsp;&nbsp; <nobr><a href=\"/vir/content/88/4/1379\"><font size=\"-1\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">[Abstract]</font></a> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <a href=\"/vir/content/88/4/1379\"><font size=\"-1\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">[Full Text]</font></a> <font size=\"-2\" face=\"arial,helvetica\"></font>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <a href=\"/vir/content/88/4/1379\"><font size=\"-1\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">[PDF]</font></a> <font size=\"-2\" face=\"arial,helvetica\"></font></nobr></font></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td nowrap=\"\"></td>\n      <td nowrap=\"\"></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>&nbsp;</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\"><font size=\"-1\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">5.</font>&nbsp;</td>\n      <td colspan=\"2\"><font size=\"-1\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">Encarnación Martínez-Salas, Almudena Pacheco, Paula Serrano, Noemi Fernandez</font></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td nowrap=\"\"></td>\n      <td nowrap=\"\"></td>\n      <th align=\"left\"><font size=\"-1\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">New insights into internal ribosome entry site elements relevant for viral gene expression</font></th>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td nowrap=\"\"></td>\n      <td nowrap=\"\"></td>\n      <td><font size=\"-1\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">J. Gen. Virol. Mar 01, 2008; 89: 611-626.<br>\n      (In \"REVIEW\")&nbsp;&nbsp; <nobr><font size=\"-1\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">[Abstract]</font> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <font size=\"-1\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">[Full Text]</font> <font size=\"-2\" face=\"arial,helvetica\"></font>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <font size=\"-1\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">[PDF]</font> <font size=\"-2\" face=\"arial,helvetica\"></font></nobr></font></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td nowrap=\"\"></td>\n      <td nowrap=\"\"></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>&nbsp;</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td colspan=\"4\" nowrap=\"\">\n        &nbsp;&nbsp; [<font size=\"-2\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">Next 5 Articles</font